Up Close: Snider's Stiebeling and Dwenger's Winkeljohn 
By WISE Web Sports October 6, 2015 Updated Oct 6, 2015 at 7:02 PM EDT 
FORT WAYNE, Ind. (21Alive) -- AWP's Dre Muhammad interviews two stars who will be on the line for the SAC title this Friday. 
Snider's Isaac Stiebeling and Dwenger's Peter Winkeljohn are this week's Up Close interviewees brought to you by Parkview Sports Medicine.
